                            <comment id="13078561" author="yuzhihong@gmail.com" created="Wed, 3 Aug 2011 02:27:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I used the patch to run through unit tests. I noticed TestRegionRebalancing was hanging:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
